OL,3,CElectronic prescriptions rolled out to
OL,4,Chelp reduce wait times in Jersey
OL,6,FPatients in may be queuing for less
OL,7,Ftime to pick up their prescriptions
OL,8,Ffollowing an electronic system which
OL,9,Fis being rolled out across the island.
OL,11,FAn electronic prescription system has
OL,12,Fbeen implemented which the government
OL,13,Fhopes will improve patient safety and
OL,14,Freduce waiting times at the Hospital
OL,15,Fpharmacy.
OL,17,FIt comes as part of the government's
OL,18,Fongoing commitment to streamline
OL,19,Fprocesses and improve safety and
OL,20,Fefficiency in Health and Community
OL,21,FServices.
