OL,3,CElectronic prescriptions rolled out to
OL,4,Chelp reduce wait times in Jersey
OL,6,FThe system will mean most patients
OL,7,Fwill no longer receive paper
OL,8,Fprescriptions.
OL,10,FThe move to paperless prescriptions is
OL,11,Fhoped to reduce waiting times by
OL,12,Fgiving the Hosptial pharmacy a chance
OL,13,Fto identify which prescriptions should
OL,14,Fbe prioritised.
OL,16,FIt is also hoped this will reduce the
OL,17,Flikelihood of prescribing errors, as
OL,18,Fwell as alerting clinicians to risks
OL,19,Frelated to drug interactions and other
OL,20,Fpotential medication problems through
OL,21,Fclinical decisions.
