OL,3,CElectronic prescriptions rolled out to
OL,4,Chelp reduce wait times in Jersey
OL,6,FPharmacy Services Manager, Kevin Smith
OL,7,Fsays: "The pharmacy dispenses around
OL,8,F800 items a day, with up to 250 people
OL,9,Fattending at the outpatient pharmacy
OL,10,Fevery working day.
OL,12,F"Electronic prescribing makes it
OL,13,Feasier and safer to screen, process,
OL,14,Fand supply medication. And because
OL,15,Fpharmacy staff are not trying to
OL,16,Fdecipher handwritten prescriptions,
OL,17,Fthe risk of medication errors is
OL,18,Freduced."
